definition.value: A cyclic carotene that is beta-carotene which the double bond between positions 7 and 8 has been hydrogenated.
A divinyl ether fatty acid that is (9Z,11E,14E,16Z)-nonadeca-9,11,14,16-tetraenoic acid in which the methylene group at position 13 has been replaced by oxygen.
A 9-HOTrE consisting of (10E,12Z,15Z)-octadecatrienoic acid in which the 9-hydroxy group has S-configuration.
